These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, water, iced-tea, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, camping, writing, puzzles
1. the person drinking water is between the person drinking sprite and the person who's hobby is camping##2
2. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
3. the person drinking water is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person drinking sprite##7
4. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | milk       | water | sprite        |
| Hobby      | writing  | camping | puzzles        | cooking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, lizard, pony, goldfish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, parkour, snowboarding, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the owner of the pony##7
2. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
3. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
4. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's sport is parkour##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | pony | lizard       | goldfish         | guinea-pig     |
| Sport   | parkour   | lacrosse | snowboarding | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, disaster, horror, drama
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, disco, d&b, rock
1. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the fan of rock##1
2. the fan of rock is somewhere between the fan of disco and the fan of salsa##7
3. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the fan of salsa is somewhere between the fan of rock and the person watching disaster movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | drama | horror | romance  |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | salsa  | rock   | disco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, skydiving, camping, drawing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, surfing, baseball, cricket
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
3. the person who's hobby is camping is the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | skydiving | board-games | drawing       | camping |
| Sport   | surfing      | skiing   | baseball | cricket  |

