.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, filmmaking, dancing, baking
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, australian, spanish, mexican
1. the mexican is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
2. the indian is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
4. the mexican is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is sudoku##7
5. the mexican is on the left of the spanish##1
6. the australian is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | dancing | sudoku   | baking | filmmaking |
| Nationality   | indian      | australian | mexican      | spanish |

