.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, coffee, cola, hot-chocolate
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, russian, indian, turkish
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the indian##1
2. the indian is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the russian is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the turkish##3
6. the turkish is somewhere between the polish and the russian##7
7. the indian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | coffee | fanta      | cola | hot-chocolate     |
| Nationality   | polish    | turkish | russian   | indian |

