.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, potato, garlic, cucumber
There are 4 different nationalities: german, malaysian, canadian, indian
1. the german is on the far left##1
2. the person eating potato is on the left of the malaysian##1
3. the person eating cucumber is on the far left or far right##3
4. the indian is somewhere between the person eating mango and the person eating garlic##7
5. the canadian is somewhere to the left of the person eating garlic##5
6. the indian is on the left or right of the canadian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | cucumber    | mango   | potato | garlic  |
| Nationality   | german | canadian | indian    | malaysian |

