2. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
3. the russian is the owner of the rat##1
4. the pakistani is somewhere between the russian and the canadian##7
5. the japanese is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
7. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani | japanese | canadian |
| Pet           | rat   | snake    | pony       | guinea-pig  |

