4. the dancer is on the right of the fan of rock##1
5. the photographer is somewhere between the fan of rock and the designer##7
6. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the fan of metal##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
