2. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of disco##1
3. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching spy movies is between the person watching family movies and the fan of jazz##2
6. the fan of dubstep is somewhere between the fan of jazz and the person watching family movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
