.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, skydiving, gardening, dancing
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, ship, tram
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person driving the ship is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere between the person driving the helicopter and the person who's hobby is gardening##7
7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | dancing | puzzles | skydiving | gardening |
| Transport   | helicopter   | tram      | jet-ski        | ship  |

