The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, d&b, classical, folk
1. the fan of d&b is in an even position##4
2. the fan of folk is somewhere between the person drinking almond-milk and the fan of classical##7
3. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
4. the fan of classical is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the fan of d&b##5
6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the fan of classical##1
7. the person drinking sprite is the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | milk   | soy-milk | sprite | almond-milk   |
| Music-Genre   | punk | classical   | folk | d&b |

