.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, turtle, goat, mouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, ship, bike, boat
1. the owner of the goat is somewhere between the person driving the tram and the owner of the turtle##7
2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
4. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
5. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | turtle    | goat | mouse     | fish |
| Transport   | bike | boat  | ship | tram |

 